A barebones library to use n20 motors with encoders as stepper motors. 


Tested with:
____________________________________________________________________________

* N20 motor with encoder 12V 60RPM
  https://robu.in/product/n20-12v-60rpm-micro-metal-gear-motor-with-encoder/

* TA6586 based motor driver
  https://robu.in/product/ta6586-based-motor-driver-module/


Credits:
____________________________________________________________________________

* Curious Scientist: For core logic of the n20 encoder
  https://curiousscientist.tech/blog/positioning-with-the-n20-miniature-geared-dc-motors
